msgctxt "784"
msgid "Quit"
msgstr "Salir"

msgctxt "789"
msgid "Cancel the order."
msgstr "Cancelar el pedido."

msgctxt "807"
msgid "Order"
msgstr "Pagar"

msgctxt "813"
msgid "Order the currently selected item.  "
msgstr "Pedir el objeto actualmente seleccionado.  "

msgctxt "850"
msgid "(I haven't picked anything.)  "
msgstr "(No he escogido nada)"

msgctxt "881"
msgid "(I'm short on cash.)  "
msgstr "(Me hace falta dinero)"

msgctxt "904"
msgid "Very well, that's %s."
msgstr "Muy bien, eso es %s."

msgctxt "926"
msgid "(I can't carry any more stuff.)"
msgstr "(No puedo llevar más cosas)."

msgctxt "958"
msgid "(They're sold out.)"
msgstr "(Están agotados)."

msgctxt "978"
msgid "The strongest supplement on the market. Will fully\n"
"restore your health."
msgstr "El suplemento más fuerte del mercado. Recuperará\n"
"completamente su salud."

msgctxt "1050"
msgid "Will fill your Heat to its maximum level. You'll be a\n"
"walking inferno!"
msgstr "Llenará tu Heat a su nivel máximo. ¡Serás un\n"
"infierno andante!"

msgctxt "1121"
msgid "Will rejuvenate your body and soul. And it'll restore \n"
"your health and Heat to their maximum levels!"
msgstr "Rejuvenecerá tu cuerpo y alma. ¡Y restaurará \n"
"tu salud y Heat a sus niveles máximos!"

msgctxt "1222"
msgid "These plastic shin guards provide light protection. \n"
"They're thin, so don't expect too much. "
msgstr "Estas espinilleras de plástico proporcionan una protección\n"
"ligera. Son delgadas, así que no esperes demasiado."

msgctxt "1316"
msgid "This black belt is special, as they say the power of its \n"
"late judo master resides within. It should give you \n"
"extra throwing strength."
msgstr "Este cinturón negro es especial, dicen que el poder de su \n"
"difunto maestro de judo reside dentro. Debería darte \n"
"fuerza extra de lanzamiento."

msgctxt "1452"
msgid "This unique weapon is designed to deliver burning\n"
"pain with deep cuts."
msgstr "Esta arma única está diseñada para hacer dolor abrasador con cortes profundos."

msgctxt "1523"
msgid "This towel brings a sense of peace to its user, \n"
"lowering their Heat."
msgstr "Esta toalla trae una sensación de paz a su usuario, \n"
"reduciendo su Heat."

msgctxt "1593"
msgid "This unusual stone refracts light in a unique way. It's\n"
"meant to be a commemorative item."
msgstr "Esta inusual piedra refracta la luz de una manera única.\n"
"Está pensada para ser un objeto conmemorativo."

msgctxt "1683"
msgid "These are steel shin guards. They'll help protect your\n"
"legs from attacks."
msgstr "Estas son espinilleras de acero. Te ayudarán a proteger\n"
"tus piernas de ataques."

msgctxt "1757"
msgid "This ring increases your physical strength more and\n"
"more as you get injured."
msgstr "Este anillo aumenta tu fuerza física cada vez más a\n"
"medida que te lesionas."

msgctxt "1834"
msgid "This is the Demon Stone, named for the hideous face\n"
"carved on it. They say it has something to do with a \n"
"deity who watches over travelers."
msgstr "Esta es la Piedra Demoníaca, llamada así por la horrible\n"
"cara tallada en ella. Dicen que tiene algo que ver con una\n"
"deidad que vela por los viajeros."

msgctxt "1974"
msgid "A bloodied cloth that has seen plenty of action in the\n"
"Coliseum. Its original wearers have bled their souls\n"
"into it."
msgstr "Un paño ensangrentado que ha visto mucha acción en el\n"
"Coliseo. Sus portadores originales han sangrado sus almas en él."

msgctxt "2091"
msgid "A mysterious power residing in this thing somehow\n"
"strengthens left-handed attacks."
msgstr "Un poder misterioso que reside en esta cosa de alguna\n"
"forma fortalece los ataques zurdos."

msgctxt "2174"
msgid "These shoes will help muffle your steps. They're often\n"
"worn by unsavory individuals to help them get out of\n"
"trouble."
msgstr "Estos zapatos te ayudarán a amortiguar tus pasos. A menudo son usado por individuos desagradables para ayudarlos a salir del problema."

msgctxt "2291"
msgid "These babies shield your entire fist. "
msgstr "Estos bebés protegen todo tu puño. "

msgctxt "2330"
msgid "This thing is surprisingly effective as a hammer."
msgstr "Esta cosa es sorprendentemente efectiva como martillo."

msgctxt "2380"
msgid "Put on this ring, and you'll have people coming at you\n"
"in droves for a chance to defeat the Champ."
msgstr "Ponte este anillo, y tendrás gente viniendo hacia ti\n"
"en masa por una oportunidad de derrotar al campeón."

msgctxt "2479"
msgid "There's something I really don't like about this bloody\n"
"binding. Be careful when you use it..."
msgstr "Hay algo que realmente me disgusta de este sarashi\n"
"sangriento. Ten cuidado al usarla..."

msgctxt "2574"
msgid "Will have a healing effect if you stand calmly during \n"
"a fight."
msgstr "Tendrás un efecto curativo si te quedas calmado durante \n"
"una pelea."

msgctxt "2638"
msgid "This is a photo of an old and influential yakuza. They \n"
"say just carrying it will awaken the bloodlust of the \n"
"people around you. "
msgstr "Esta es una foto de un yakuza antiguo e influyente.\n"
"Dicen que solo llevarla despertará la sed de sangre\n"
"de las personas que te rodean."

msgctxt "2769"
msgid "This ornate blade is etched with a beautiful and \n"
"intricate carp pattern. Its craftsmanship is of the \n"
"highest quality."
msgstr "Esta Espada Ornamentada está grabada con un\n"
"hermoso y detallado patrón de carpas. Su artesanía\n"
"es de la más alta calidad."

msgctxt "2889"
msgid "Grab an enemy while wearing these to sap their \n"
"strength and charge your Heat up."
msgstr "Agarra a un enemigo mientras los usas para despejar\n"
"su fuerza y ​​cargar tu Heat."

msgctxt "2971"
msgid "This chain mail is said to confer upon its wearer the \n"
"protection of a divine dragon... or something. It's \n"
"really well-made, anyway."
msgstr "Se dice que esta cota de malla confiere a su portador la\n"
"protección de un dragón divino... o algo así. Está \n"
"realmente bien hecha, de todos modos."

